Name: Elon Simulator 2019
About the game: Elon Simulator 2019 is a dynamic shooting game in the space. Feel as a Starman on it’s journey to the Mars! Shoot the space objects to win or simply avoid them to staying alive for as long as you can. Different objects bumping into you would cause different levels of damages and - as you’ll soon find out - some of them are much more dangerous than others. The game currently features: Exciting gameplay Variety of space objects Dynamic soundtrack And once you'll reach the Mars continue the journey with our next game /
